    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span>\n<h3>Problem Description</h3>\n<p>There are <b>N</b> students in a class.The lazy teacher randomly gives a number(Lets call this the 'Class Random Number' CRN)to each of the students.<br />\nTo keep them busy for a long time she gives the following work.<br />\nFor each student,<br /><br />\n1.Calculate the sum of all the other students' Class Random Number(excluding yours).<br /><br />\n2.Once every student is done with step 1, set the sum obtained from step 1 as your new 'Class Random Number'.<br /><br />\n3.Repeat step 1.<br />\n</p>\n<p>\u00a0The teacher instructs the students to repeat the process 'T' number of times, hoping that it would take a very long time. Much to her suprise, one of the students claims that<br />\nhe has completed the calculation and that he knows the 'Class Random Number' of all the students after 'T' iterations.The teacher thus asks the CRN of Q students.You, being<br />\nthat class student are going to write a program to complete the given task.Since the numbers can be very large, output the answer mod 1000000007 (10e9 + 7)\n</p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>The first line of input contains the number of students <b>N</b>.<br />\nThe next line of input contains <b>N</b> space separated integers <b>Ai</b>, where i denotes the 'Class Random Number' of student i.<br />\nThe next line of input contains <b>T</b>, the number of iterations involved in the process.<br />\nThe next line of input contains <b>Q</b>, the number of queries the teacher is about to ask.<br />\n<b>Q</b> lines follow, each containing a single integer <b>Si</b>, indicating the ith student.(1 indexed)</p>\n<ul>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>Output description.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>For each query Si, output in a new line, the 'Class Random Number' of Student Si after 'T' iterations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<p>Should contain all the constraints on the input data that you may have. Format it like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>1000</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>Ai</b> \u2264 <b>100000</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>T</b> \u2264 <b>1000000000</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>Q</b> \u2264 <b>100</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>Si</b> \u2264 <b>N</b></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n4\n1 2 3 4\n4\n3\n2\n1\n3\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n202\n201\n203\n\n</pre><p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Explanation</h3>\n<p>After 1st iteration, the 'CRN's would be 9 8 7 6<br /><br />\nAfter 2nd iteration, the 'CRN's would be 21 22 23 24<br /><br />\nAfter 3rd iteration, the 'CRN's would be 69 68 67 66<br /><br />\nAfter 4th iteration, the 'CRN's would be 201 202 203 204<br /></p>\n",
